// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0157 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a01ec519-d162-55df-adb4-3216e8566791

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*")
